  "texts": [
    "Nagata et al.",
    "developed a convulsion prediction model based on heart rate variability to predict drug-induced convulsions.",
    "Their model is built based on an anomaly detection algorithm named multivariate statistical process control [168].",
    "Zhang et al.",
    "presented an enhanced SVM model to predict the seizure liability of chemicals, which was characterized by its cost-effectiveness, expeditiousness, and superior accuracy [161]."
  ]
}